<p>Unless otherwise agreed in writing, delivery dates provided by us are estimates only. We will make reasonable efforts to deliver in accordance with such dates; however, Turaja will not be liable for failure to deliver as estimated. Unless otherwise agreed in writing by us, Goods shall be packaged according to our standards and practices.</p>
